TITLE: Creating a Basic Plate Editor
DESCRIPTION: Implements a minimal Plate editor setup with the essential components. The Plate component manages editor state while PlateContent renders the editable content area.

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import {
  usePlateEditor,
  Plate,
  PlateContent,
} from '@udecode/plate/react';

export default function BasicEditor() {
  const editor = usePlateEditor();

  return (
    <Plate editor={editor}>
      <PlateContent placeholder="Type..." />
    </Plate>
  );
}
```

