TITLE: Table Plugin Option Renaming
DESCRIPTION: Breaking change in the TablePlugin where the disableUnsetSingleColSize option has been renamed and inverted into enableUnsetSingleColSize in version 20.0.0.

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// Before
createTablePlugin({
  disableUnsetSingleColSize: true // or false
})

// After
createTablePlugin({
  // if using disableUnsetSingleColSize: true, the option can be removed
  // if using disableUnsetSingleColSize: false, use:
  enableUnsetSingleColSize: true
})
```

