TITLE: Migrating from prismjs to highlight.js in CodeBlockPlugin
DESCRIPTION: Code snippet showing how to configure CodeBlockPlugin with highlight.js and lowlight after the migration from prismjs in version 46.0.0.

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { all, createLowlight } from 'lowlight';

const lowlight = createLowlight(all);

CodeBlockPlugin.configure({
  options: {
    lowlight,
  },
});
```
